{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.1","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:1","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.031.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Invasion de Sanch\u00e9rib, roi d\u2019Assyrie, et destruction de son arm\u00e9e<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-8: cf. (2 R 18:13-16. \u00c9s 36:1.) (\u00c9s 10:5, etc.; 22:1-14.) Ps 118:6-9.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Apr\u00e8s ces choses et ces actes de fid\u00e9lit\u00e9, parut Sanch\u00e9rib, roi d\u2019Assyrie, qui p\u00e9n\u00e9tra en Juda, et assi\u00e9gea les villes fortes, dans l\u2019intention de s\u2019en emparer.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.2","name":"2 Chroniques 32:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.31.21","name":"2 Chroniques 31:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.31.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.2","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:2","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>\u00c9z\u00e9chias, voyant que Sanch\u00e9rib \u00e9tait venu et qu\u2019il se proposait d\u2019attaquer J\u00e9rusalem,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.3","name":"2 Chroniques 32:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.1","name":"2 Chroniques 32:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.3","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:3","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>tint conseil avec ses chefs et ses hommes vaillants, afin de boucher les sources d\u2019eau qui \u00e9taient hors de la ville; et ils furent de son avis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.4","name":"2 Chroniques 32:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.2","name":"2 Chroniques 32:2","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.4","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:4","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Une foule de gens se rassembl\u00e8rent, et ils bouch\u00e8rent toutes les sources et le ruisseau qui coule au milieu de la contr\u00e9e. Pourquoi, disaient-ils, les rois d\u2019Assyrie trouveraient-ils \u00e0 leur arriv\u00e9e des eaux en abondance?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.5","name":"2 Chroniques 32:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.3","name":"2 Chroniques 32:3","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.5","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:5","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>\u00c9z\u00e9chias prit courage; il reconstruisit la muraille qui \u00e9tait en ruine et l\u2019\u00e9leva jusqu\u2019aux tours, b\u00e2tit un autre mur en dehors, fortifia Millo dans la cit\u00e9 de David, et pr\u00e9para une quantit\u00e9 d\u2019armes et de boucliers.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.6","name":"2 Chroniques 32:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.4","name":"2 Chroniques 32:4","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.6","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:6","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Il donna des chefs militaires au peuple, et les r\u00e9unit aupr\u00e8s de lui sur la place de la porte de la ville. S\u2019adressant \u00e0 leur c\u0153ur, il dit:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.7","name":"2 Chroniques 32:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.5","name":"2 Chroniques 32:5","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.7","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:7","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Fortifiez-vous et ayez du courage! Ne craignez point et ne soyez point effray\u00e9s devant le roi d\u2019Assyrie et devant toute la multitude qui est avec lui; car avec nous il y a plus qu\u2019avec lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.8","name":"2 Chroniques 32:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.6","name":"2 Chroniques 32:6","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.8","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:8","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Avec lui est un bras de chair, et avec nous l\u2019\u00c9ternel, notre Dieu, qui nous aidera et qui combattra pour nous. Le peuple eut confiance dans les paroles d\u2019\u00c9z\u00e9chias, roi de Juda.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.9","name":"2 Chroniques 32:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.7","name":"2 Chroniques 32:7","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.9","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:9","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.010,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 9-19: cf. (2 R 18:17, etc. \u00c9s 36:2, etc.) Ps 42:11, 12.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>\n    Apr\u00e8s cela, Sanch\u00e9rib, roi d\u2019Assyrie, envoya ses serviteurs \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, pendant qu\u2019il \u00e9tait devant Lakis avec toutes ses forces; il les envoya vers \u00c9z\u00e9chias, roi de Juda, et vers tous ceux de Juda qui \u00e9taient \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, pour leur dire:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.10","name":"2 Chroniques 32:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.8","name":"2 Chroniques 32:8","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.10","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:10","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Ainsi parle Sanch\u00e9rib, roi d\u2019Assyrie: Sur quoi repose votre confiance, pour que vous restiez \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem dans la d\u00e9tresse?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.11","name":"2 Chroniques 32:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.9","name":"2 Chroniques 32:9","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.11","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:11","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>\u00c9z\u00e9chias ne vous abuse-t-il pas pour vous livrer \u00e0 la mort par la famine et par la soif, quand il dit: L\u2019\u00c9ternel, notre Dieu, nous sauvera de la main du roi d\u2019Assyrie?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.12","name":"2 Chroniques 32:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.10","name":"2 Chroniques 32:10","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.12","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:12","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>N\u2019est-ce pas lui, \u00c9z\u00e9chias, qui a fait dispara\u00eetre les hauts lieux et les autels de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et qui a donn\u00e9 cet ordre \u00e0 Juda et \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem: Vous vous prosternerez devant un seul autel, et vous y offrirez les parfums?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.13","name":"2 Chroniques 32:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.11","name":"2 Chroniques 32:11","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.13","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:13","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Ne savez-vous pas ce que nous avons fait, moi et mes p\u00e8res, \u00e0 tous les peuples des autres pays? Les dieux des nations de ces pays ont-ils pu d\u00e9livrer leurs pays de ma main?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.14","name":"2 Chroniques 32:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.12","name":"2 Chroniques 32:12","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.14","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:14","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Parmi tous les dieux de ces nations que mes p\u00e8res ont extermin\u00e9es, quel est celui qui a pu d\u00e9livrer son peuple de ma main, pour que votre Dieu puisse vous d\u00e9livrer de ma main?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.15","name":"2 Chroniques 32:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.13","name":"2 Chroniques 32:13","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.15","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:15","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Qu\u2019\u00c9z\u00e9chias ne vous s\u00e9duise donc point et qu\u2019il ne vous abuse point ainsi; ne vous fiez pas \u00e0 lui! Car aucun dieu d\u2019aucune nation ni d\u2019aucun royaume n\u2019a pu d\u00e9livrer son peuple de ma main et de la main de mes p\u00e8res: combien moins votre Dieu vous d\u00e9livrera-t-il de ma main?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.16","name":"2 Chroniques 32:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.14","name":"2 Chroniques 32:14","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.16","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:16","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Les serviteurs de Sanch\u00e9rib parl\u00e8rent encore contre l\u2019\u00c9ternel Dieu, et contre \u00c9z\u00e9chias, son serviteur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.17","name":"2 Chroniques 32:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.15","name":"2 Chroniques 32:15","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.17","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:17","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Et il envoya une lettre insultante pour l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, en s\u2019exprimant ainsi contre lui: De m\u00eame que les dieux des nations des autres pays n\u2019ont pu d\u00e9livrer leur peuple de ma main, de m\u00eame le Dieu d\u2019\u00c9z\u00e9chias ne d\u00e9livrera pas son peuple de ma main.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.18","name":"2 Chroniques 32:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.16","name":"2 Chroniques 32:16","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.18","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:18","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Les serviteurs de Sanch\u00e9rib cri\u00e8rent \u00e0 haute voix en langue juda\u00efque, afin de jeter l\u2019effroi et l\u2019\u00e9pouvante parmi le peuple de J\u00e9rusalem qui \u00e9tait sur la muraille, et de pouvoir ainsi s\u2019emparer de la ville.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.19","name":"2 Chroniques 32:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.17","name":"2 Chroniques 32:17","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.19","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:19","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Ils parl\u00e8rent du Dieu de J\u00e9rusalem comme des dieux des peuples de la terre, ouvrages de mains d\u2019homme.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.20","name":"2 Chroniques 32:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.18","name":"2 Chroniques 32:18","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.20","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:20","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.021,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 20-23: cf. (2 R 19. \u00c9s 37.) Ps 18:51; 76:2, etc.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>\n    Le roi \u00c9z\u00e9chias et le proph\u00e8te \u00c9sa\u00efe, fils d\u2019Amots, se mirent \u00e0 prier \u00e0 ce sujet, et ils cri\u00e8rent au ciel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.21","name":"2 Chroniques 32:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.19","name":"2 Chroniques 32:19","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.21","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:21","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Alors l\u2019\u00c9ternel envoya un ange, qui extermina dans le camp du roi d\u2019Assyrie tous les vaillants hommes, les princes et les chefs. Et le roi confus retourna dans son pays. Il entra dans la maison de son dieu, et l\u00e0 ceux qui \u00e9taient sortis de ses entrailles le firent tomber par l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.22","name":"2 Chroniques 32:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.20","name":"2 Chroniques 32:20","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.22","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:22","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Ainsi l\u2019\u00c9ternel sauva \u00c9z\u00e9chias et les habitants de J\u00e9rusalem de la main de Sanch\u00e9rib, roi d\u2019Assyrie, et de la main de tous, et il les prot\u00e9gea contre ceux qui les entouraient.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.23","name":"2 Chroniques 32:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.21","name":"2 Chroniques 32:21","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.23","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:23","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Beaucoup de gens apport\u00e8rent dans J\u00e9rusalem des offrandes \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et de riches pr\u00e9sents \u00e0 \u00c9z\u00e9chias, roi de Juda, qui depuis lors fut \u00e9lev\u00e9 aux yeux de toutes les nations.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.24","name":"2 Chroniques 32:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.22","name":"2 Chroniques 32:22","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.24","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:24","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.025,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 24-33: cf. (2 R 20. \u00c9s 38; 39.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>\n    En ce temps-l\u00e0, \u00c9z\u00e9chias fut malade \u00e0 la mort. Il fit une pri\u00e8re \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9ternel; et l\u2019\u00c9ternel lui adressa la parole, et lui accorda un prodige.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.25","name":"2 Chroniques 32:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.23","name":"2 Chroniques 32:23","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.25","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:25","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Mais \u00c9z\u00e9chias ne r\u00e9pondit point au bienfait qu\u2019il avait re\u00e7u, car son c\u0153ur s\u2019\u00e9leva; et la col\u00e8re de l\u2019\u00c9ternel fut sur lui, sur Juda et sur J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.26","name":"2 Chroniques 32:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.24","name":"2 Chroniques 32:24","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.26","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:26","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Alors \u00c9z\u00e9chias, du sein de son orgueil, s\u2019humilia avec les habitants de J\u00e9rusalem, et la col\u00e8re de l\u2019\u00c9ternel ne vint pas sur eux pendant la vie d\u2019\u00c9z\u00e9chias.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.27","name":"2 Chroniques 32:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.25","name":"2 Chroniques 32:25","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.27","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:27","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>\u00c9z\u00e9chias eut beaucoup de richesses et de gloire. Il se fit des tr\u00e9sors d\u2019argent, d\u2019or, de pierres pr\u00e9cieuses, d\u2019aromates, de boucliers et de tous les objets qu\u2019on peut d\u00e9sirer;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.28","name":"2 Chroniques 32:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.26","name":"2 Chroniques 32:26","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.28","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:28","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>des magasins pour les produits en bl\u00e9, en mo\u00fbt et en huile, des cr\u00e8ches pour toute esp\u00e8ce de b\u00e9tail, et des \u00e9tables pour les troupeaux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.29","name":"2 Chroniques 32:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.27","name":"2 Chroniques 32:27","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.29","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:29","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>Il se b\u00e2tit des villes, et il eut en abondance des troupeaux de menu et de gros b\u00e9tail; car Dieu lui avait donn\u00e9 des biens consid\u00e9rables.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.30","name":"2 Chroniques 32:30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.28","name":"2 Chroniques 32:28","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.30","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:30","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Ce fut aussi lui, \u00c9z\u00e9chias, qui boucha l\u2019issue sup\u00e9rieure des eaux de Guihon, et les conduisit en bas vers l\u2019occident de la cit\u00e9 de David. \u00c9z\u00e9chias r\u00e9ussit dans toutes ses entreprises.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.31","name":"2 Chroniques 32:31","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.29","name":"2 Chroniques 32:29","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.31","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:31","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Cependant, lorsque les chefs de Babylone envoy\u00e8rent des messagers aupr\u00e8s de lui pour s\u2019informer du prodige qui avait eu lieu dans le pays, Dieu l\u2019abandonna pour l\u2019\u00e9prouver, afin de conna\u00eetre tout ce qui \u00e9tait dans son c\u0153ur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32:32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.30","name":"2 Chroniques 32:30","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.32","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:32","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.032.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>Le reste des actions d\u2019\u00c9z\u00e9chias, et ses \u0153uvres de pi\u00e9t\u00e9, cela est \u00e9crit dans la vision du proph\u00e8te \u00c9sa\u00efe, fils d\u2019Amots, dans le livre des rois de Juda et d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.33","name":"2 Chroniques 32:33","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.31","name":"2 Chroniques 32:31","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.33","label":"","reference":"2 Chroniques 32:33","prev_osis_id":"2Chr.032.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Chr.033.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"2Chr.32.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>\u00c9z\u00e9chias se coucha avec ses p\u00e8res, et on l\u2019enterra dans le lieu le plus \u00e9lev\u00e9 des s\u00e9pulcres des fils de David; tout Juda et les habitants de J\u00e9rusalem lui rendirent honneur \u00e0 sa mort. Et Manass\u00e9, son fils, r\u00e9gna \u00e0 sa place.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.33.1","name":"2 Chroniques 33:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.33.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Chr.32.32","name":"2 Chroniques 32:32","id":"fra-LSG:2Chr.32.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb5754ab2.48706847');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb5754ab2.48706847\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb5754ab2.48706847","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb5754ab2.48706847'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb5754ab2.48706847\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}